casebody.data:
Louis A. Zuch, Respondent, v. Philip Bander, Appellant.

Order unanimously affirmed, with $20 costs and disbursements, with leave to the defendant to answer within ten days after service of the order, with notice of entry thereof, on payment of said costs. No opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., Dore, Cohn, Callahan and Peek, JJ.
